{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dreamwalker is a top-down story RPG game with deckbuilding combat.</strong>\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a journey through dreams and nightmares in Dreamwalker, a 2D top-down RPG set in a mesmerizing pixel art world. You are a wandering traveler, drawn to a small village shrouded in mystery and cursed by an ancient evil.     </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udccf <strong>Deckbuilding Combat</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Choose your starter deck</strong> and forge your own playstyle as you collect, upgrade, and craft a unique deck tailored to your strategy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Visit merchants</strong> to buy, sell, upgrade, and trade up cards to refine your deck.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>200+ unique cards</strong> across 4 rarities (Common, Rare, Epic, Legendary), featuring upgradable and combinable effects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Turn-based combat with animated enemies. Face different elemental foes with special Moves: Stuns, poison, burn, deck disruption, and more - forcing you to adapt as you progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283940/extras/DW_cbt.gif?t=1739613713\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udca4 <strong>Enter a World of Living Dreams</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each villager\u2019s mind is its <strong>own world</strong>\u2014a haunted castle, a shifting marketplace, or a forest of glowing memories.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each dream holds <strong>secrets, challenges, and unexpected allies</strong> waiting to be discovered.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete quests, solve intricate puzzles, and shape the story with your decisions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earn powerful new cards and Dreamtokens to strengthen your deck.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283940/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739613713","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283940/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739613713","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283940/f7db291272fa570d684bf833d516e90cd669deab/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739613713","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283940/f7db291272fa570d684bf833d516e90cd669deab/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739613713","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3431780,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dreamwalker is a top-down story RPG game with deckbuilding combat.</strong>\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a journey through dreams and nightmares in Dreamwalker, a 2D top-down RPG set in a mesmerizing pixel art world. You are a wandering traveler, drawn to a small village shrouded in mystery and cursed by an ancient evil.     </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udccf <strong>Deckbuilding Combat</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Choose your starter deck</strong> and forge your own playstyle as you collect, upgrade, and craft a unique deck tailored to your strategy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Visit merchants</strong> to buy, sell, upgrade, and trade up cards to refine your deck.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>200+ unique cards</strong> across 4 rarities (Common, Rare, Epic, Legendary), featuring upgradable and combinable effects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"